    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个典型的Git工作流，展示主干开发和特性分支的合并过程。先有两个初始提交在main分支上，然后从main切出一个develop分支做功能开发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "commit",
        "branch develop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，develop分支从main的第二个commit切出来对吧？然后develop上需要几个commit？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch develop",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，develop上做两个commit，模拟功能开发完成。然后切回main分支，把develop合并进来，最后再补一个commit表示发布后的修复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "merge develop",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画主干：main上两个commit，然后branch develop，checkout到develop，上面两个commit。现在develop开发完了，我切回main准备merge。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "checkout develop",
        "commit",
        "checkout main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，确认一下merge的方向——是main去合并develop，不是develop合并main吧？我们要的是功能分支合回主干。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge develop",
        "main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，当前在main分支上执行merge develop，这样develop的两个commit就会合并到main。合并后再加一个commit，整个流程就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge develop",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "结构没问题了。不过我在想，develop分支合并后还要保留吗？还是画成合并后主线继续往前就行？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "按标准Git图来画，develop分支在merge后作为历史保留，但不再延伸。main继续向前一个commit，这样最清晰。图已经画好了，您看下这个结构。",
